Class ApplicantDB

java.lang.Object
database.dataclass.users.ApplicantDB
public class ApplicantDB extends Object
The ApplicantDB class manages the database of applicants. It provides methods to initialize, update, retrieve, and add applicants. The data is persisted using file operations.
